with open fire, you’ll need gridiron, and you might spill soy sauce on stove top.So it’s a little bit pain in the neck.

00:00:31.420 --> 00:00:36.740
I’m showing you how to make Yaki Onigiri with frying pan today.

00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:39.220
Let’s get started.

00:04:04.700 --> 00:04:09.160
It’s so easy to make, so please try this out at home.

00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:15.880
