00:04:16.080 --> 00:04:19.380
I’m no longer using microwave by the way.

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:25.080
Try not to spread soy sauce right after put Yaki Onigiti onto frying pan.

00:04:25.380 --> 00:04:33.040
